law.text:
This subtitle does not apply to:
An electronic device that is in compliance with federal law;
Any distribution operation or activity performed in a factory, warehouse, or establishment, or, in the course of surface transportation, at a port facility as defined in § 6-101 of the Transportation Article;
A vehicle as defined in § 11-176 of the Transportation Article, a product or part for use in a vehicle, or transportation equipment; and
A product or material excluded by federal law.
